===Etymology===
Borrowed in 1816 from {{etyl|fr|en}} {{m|fr|sémaphore}}, coined in French from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|σῆμα||sign}}, and {{m|grc||-φωρος|bearing, bearer}}, from {{m|grc|φέρω||to bear, carry}}.

